OL,3,C'Ahead of his time': Families honour
OL,4,Cbody donors at Leicester memorial
OL,6,F"Mum was very matter of fact," Michael
OL,7,FHollis has told ITV News, remembering
OL,8,Fthe day she explained why she wanted
OL,9,Fto donate her body to science.
OL,11,FHis mother, Lillian, was one of 1,702
OL,12,Fpeople to give their bodies to
OL,13,FLeicester Medical School since its
OL,14,Fdonation programme began 50 years ago.
OL,16,FHe recalls her saying: "how else are
OL,17,Fdoctors going to learn?"
