OL,3,C'Ahead of his time': Families honour
OL,4,Cbody donors at Leicester memorial
OL,6,FHer decision left a legacy that goes
OL,7,Ffar beyond her family, giving medical
OL,8,Fstudents a chance to learn in ways no
OL,9,Ftextbook ever could.
OL,11,FNow, Michael has signed up to do the
OL,12,Fsame.
OL,14,F"I was diagnosed with advanced
OL,15,Fprostate cancer last year and it helps
OL,16,Fto galvanise the mind on quite a few
OL,17,Ffronts," he said.
