OL,6,FMr Hollis said: "Mum did it, and in
OL,7,Fthe course of my treatment at
OL,8,FLeicester Royal Infirmary and
OL,9,FLeicester General I met some amazing
OL,10,Fsurgeons, doctors, nurses.
OL,12,F"I was really well looked after and I
OL,13,Fjust thought if something good can
OL,14,Fcome out of it, it's an opportunity to
OL,15,Fgive my body to the programme as well
OL,16,Fwhen it comes to it."
