OL,3,C'Ahead of his time': Families honour
OL,4,Cbody donors at Leicester memorial
OL,6,FAt a special memorial service hosted
OL,7,Fby the University of Leicester,
OL,8,Ffamilies gathered to honour those who
OL,9,Fhad donated their bodies to medical
OL,10,Fscience.
OL,12,FAmong them was Shilla Naik, whose
OL,13,Ffather Genti quietly signed up back in
OL,14,F2013. His family only found out after
OL,15,Fhe died in 2022.
