OL,3,C'Ahead of his time': Families honour
OL,4,Cbody donors at Leicester memorial
OL,6,F"He was ahead of his time, we are so
OL,7,Fproud of him," Shilla told ITV News
OL,8,FCentral, before adding: "In our
OL,9,Fcommunity, it's not the kind of thing
OL,10,Fthat is spoken about or discussed or
OL,11,Fpromoted, so he was ahead of his time.
OL,13,F"We're all super proud of him."
OL,15,FAfter his passing, more than 100
OL,16,Ffriends and relatives attended a
OL,17,Fmemorial service. Shilla said her
OL,18,Ffather's decision has already inspired
OL,19,Fothers.
