OL,3,C'Ahead of his time': Families honour
OL,4,Cbody donors at Leicester memorial
OL,6,F"We promoted the selfless act that my
OL,7,Fdad did, donating his body, and I know
OL,8,Fof five people who've signed up for it.
OL,10,F"It's not for everybody because that
OL,11,Floved one is in the care of the
OL,12,Funiversity, so there's that long
OL,13,Fperiod of time where you can't have
OL,14,Fhim back, so that can be hard.
OL,16,F"I've had strict instruction from my
OL,17,Fdaughter that I'm not allowed to do
OL,18,Fthat - but she's happy for me to be a
OL,19,Fblood donor.
