OL,3,C'Ahead of his time': Families honour
OL,4,Cbody donors at Leicester memorial
OL,6,F"It's not for everybody, but I do
OL,7,Fencourage people from all communities
OL,8,Fto have a look into it. It's amazing
OL,9,Fthe value it gives to these students."
OL,11,FLeicester's body donation programme
OL,12,Fhas trained thousands of doctors and
OL,13,Fsurgeons over the last half-century.
OL,15,FFor families like the Hollises and the
OL,16,FNaiks, it has also offered something
OL,17,Fmore personal - the pride that their
OL,18,Floved one's final act will help
OL,19,Ftransform medicine for generations to
OL,20,Fcome.
